OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776777070
OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest jazz bands play
OL,4,Clast gig after 77 years performing
OL,6,FVictoria Grimes went to meet the
OL,7,Fmembers of one of the UK's oldest jazz
OL,8,Fbands.
OL,10,FOne of the UK's oldest jazz bands has
OL,11,Fplayed their final gig after 77 years
OL,12,Fof performing.
OL,14,FThe Merseysippi Jazz Band - originally
OL,15,Fknown as The Wallasey Rhythm Kings -
OL,16,Fwere famously the first act to play at
OL,17,FLiverpool's Cavern Club in 1957, four
OL,18,Fyears before The Beatles.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
