PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776777070
OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest jazz bands play
OL,4,Clast gig after 77 years performing
OL,6,FThey were formed Valentines Day in
OL,7,F1949, but following the death of
OL,8,Ffounding member Frank Robinson in 2013
OL,9,Fand as the remaining members enter
OL,10,Ftheir 90s, they have decided to bring
OL,11,Fthe band to an end.
OL,13,FMr Robinson was the brains behind the
OL,14,Fbands name, suggesting they combine
OL,15,Fthe Mersey and Mississippi river names.
OL,17,FHe was the last original member still
OL,18,Fplaying with the band, and died at
OL,19,FWhiston Hospital on December 30, 2012,
OL,20,Ffollowing a fall at his home in Roby
OL,21,Fearlier in the month.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
