PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776777070
OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest jazz bands play
OL,4,Clast gig after 77 years performing
OL,6,FThey became the longest running band
OL,7,Fin English history.
OL,9,FThe seven original members played
OL,10,Ftheir first gig as the Merseysippi
OL,11,FJazz Band at the Grosvenor Ballroom,
OL,12,Fin Wallasey, in an event billed as
OL,13,F"Merseyside's First Jazz Band Ball."
OL,14,FThey went on to play on the same bill
OL,15,Fas Louis Armstrong at Liverpool
OL,16,FStadium in 1956.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
