PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776777070
OL,3,COne of the UK's oldest jazz bands play
OL,4,Clast gig after 77 years performing
OL,6,FThey have loyal fans who watch them
OL,7,Fperform every week, one of their fans
OL,8,Fsaid: "They played with everybody. You
OL,9,Fcan hear it now can't you? Just the
OL,10,Fjoy that they bring to a room."
OL,12,F91-year-old trumpet player John joined
OL,13,Fthe band in 1970 but he said it's a
OL,14,F"sigh of relief" to be finishing after
OL,15,Fall those years.
OL,17,FMerseysippi Jazz Band played their
OL,18,Ffinal gig at Aigburth Arms hotel in
OL,19,FAigburth on Monday, 20 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
